<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the shrapnel damage of this item's passive ability was unintentionally getting attack damage per level added to its damage.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fate now specifies that it does not propagate effects that are listed as applying only to the primary target.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 9 (August 15, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The range at which the projectiles will bounce to other targets has been reduced to 375, down from 450.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 8 (August 09, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The secondary projectiles of this item have had their damage reduced to 40% of the primary basic attack, down from 50%.</li><li>Fixed a bug where the secondary projectiles could independently critically strike.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 1 (June 06, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The Collateral Damage passive has been redesigned. The damage caused by the projectiles is now 50% of the damage dealt by the initial attack instead of a flat value equal to 60% of your attack damage. Additionally, the projectiles will now proc other item effects and on-hit effects.</li></ul>